Cheap. Fast. Hole in the wall. If your looking for a good deal pass by here. There is an $8 card minimum so bring cash for the lunch special or be willing to pay more. All lunch specials are $5.75. They also serve American food at very affordable prices.  The interior is a bit off putting but I can put it past me for the value. If you want to sit down and eat, Takoma-Piney park is just 5 minutes away and they offer an elevated deck with shaded picnic tables that overlooks Maple Ave. and the surrounding neighborhood.
